Stumbling into people and exclaiming in a tearful voice 'pardon, pardon!' and still stumbling into people and trying not to see their faces, Luzhin looked for his wife, and when he finally caught sight of her he seized her by the elbow from behind, so that she started and turned around; but at first he was unable to say anything, he was puffing too much. 'What's the matter?' she asked anxiously. 'Let's go, let's go,' he muttered, still holding her by the elbow. 'Calm down, please, L